cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.CL

This paper deals with the presence and visibility of Latin American repositories in Google and Google Scholar, which involves issues related to digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), cryptography (cs.CR), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper discusses the indexing ratio and visibility indicators of these repositories, which are relevant to the fields of computer science and information science.
